	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm building my GB dev environment. So far I have GB Tile and Map builders for backgrounds and GBDK for code. However I have yet to see good editor for sprites. Of course since I am using GBDK, it should export to format usable by it (preferably C sources, just like tile/map builder). Also ability to life display animation is good as well.

		

