		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I've also looked everywhere for good graphic tools for Gameboy. This might not be exactly what you are looking for but it can convert PNG to Gameboy graphics (z80-source, GBDK C-source or binary) so you can use your favourite image editor for drawing. You should be able to do sprites as well.<br /><br />Pic2Tiles <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://gbdev.gg8.se/forums/viewtopic.php?id=155">http://gbdev.gg8.se/forums/viewtopic.php?id=155</a><!-- m -->

		

